{"id":147325,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/叙利亚多名作家和记者对国家的暴力行为发出谴责/","date":"2011-04-24T23:30:30Z","modified":"2011-04-24T23:30:30Z","title":"叙利亚多名作家和记者对国家的暴力行为发出谴责","content":"<div>\n<p>大马士革</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>叙利亚100多名作家和记者对国家权力机器采用暴力对付和平示威者发出强烈谴责。他们在一份声明中还对国家媒体关于示威活动的倾向性报道提出批评。人权组织“人权观察”要求对阿萨德政府采取制裁措施。据目击者和反对派小组掌握的信息，自周五以来，超过130人在示威活动和送葬活动中被打死。据人权人士说，在大马士革、霍姆斯(Homs)和其他不少城市中，有数十名反对党人士遭逮捕。英国政府呼吁所有在叙利亚的英国公民，立即离开这个国家。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C6511862%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E5%AF%B9%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categori